liblightning is a simple C library for playing audio samples with JACK on Linux systems.

API documentation is available at http://sorahan.net/liblightning

Features
* Play any file format supported by libsndfile
* Control over playback speed and gain



Build
=====

Dependencies:
* jack
* libsndfile
* libsamplerate

On ubuntu-based systems you can do
# apt-get install libjack-dev libsndfile1-dev libsamplerate0-dev

Then do
# make
# make install



If you wish to contribute, see CONTRIBUTING.